            <p>We collect information you directly provide to us, including:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Account Information:</strong> Business name, email address, phone number, and password when you register</li>
                <li><strong>Business Profile:</strong> Business type, operating hours, address, and logo</li>
                <li><strong>Queue Configuration:</strong> Queue names, service types, and operational settings</li>
                <li><strong>Customer Information:</strong> Names and phone numbers of customers joining queues</li>
                <li><strong>Communication Data:</strong> Feedback, support requests, and correspondence with us</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h3>2.2 Information Collected Automatically</h3>
            <p>When you use our Service, we automatically collect:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Queue statistics, wait times, service durations, and customer flow patterns</li>
                <li><strong>Device Information:</strong> Browser type, operating system, device type, and screen resolution</li>
                <li><strong>Log Data:</strong> IP address, access times, pages viewed, and actions taken within the Service</li>
                <li><strong>Cookies:</strong> Session cookies to maintain your login state and preferences</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h3>2.3 Information from Third Parties</h3>
            <p>During the pilot phase, we do not collect information from third-party sources.</p>
            
            <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
            
