            <p>We use the collected information to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Provide and maintain the queue management service</li>
                <li>Process customer queue entries and notifications</li>
                <li>Generate analytics and reports for your business</li>
                <li>Communicate service updates and important notices</li>
                <li>Respond to support requests and feedback</li>
                <li>Improve and develop new features</li>
            </ul>
            
