                <li><strong>Legal Requirements:</strong> When required by law or to protect rights and safety</li>
                <li><strong>Business Transfers:</strong> In connection with a merger or acquisition (users will be notified)</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h2>5. Data Storage and Security</h2>
            
            <h3>5.1 Storage Location</h3>
            <p>Your data is stored on secure cloud servers. During the pilot phase, data is primarily stored in development environments with appropriate security measures.</p>
            
            <h3>5.2 Security Measures</h3>
            <p>We implement industry-standard security measures including:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Encryption of data in transit (HTTPS/TLS)</li>
                <li>Encrypted password storage using bcrypt</li>
                <li>Regular security updates and patches</li>
                <li>Access controls and authentication</li>
                <li>Regular backups (during pilot phase, backup frequency may vary)</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h3>5.3 Data Retention</h3>
            <p>We retain your data for as long as your account is active. During the pilot phase:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Queue entry data: Retained for 6 months for analytics</li>
                <li>Account data: Retained until account deletion</li>
                <li>Log data: Retained for 3 months</li>
                <li>We may reset test data with advance notice</li>
            </ul>
            
